Simple plasmoid for fast translation of a word at http://www.leo.org (and others...). 
Click on the icon to search for the content of the clipboard at leo.org
or many other sites using your standard browser. 
Change the translation-language by right-clicking on the icon.

Requirements:
KDE4 >= 4.2

Features:
- translating the clipboard contents directly after clicking on the icon or activating keyboard shortcut;
- entering of the query in a text-field instead of using the clipboard;
- many other search engines integrated (pons.de, wikipedia, google, open dictionary, etc...);
- easy configuring of new search engines
- automatic download of icons for the search engines
- optimized to save clicks!

Availble languages for translation at leo.org:
english - german
french - german
spanish - german
italian - german
chinese - german

